      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's mostly just the wheezing and itchy eyes from being outside. i dont have my inhaler on me right now, but i have some zyrtec in my bag. if i take a couple of them it should clear up the breathing issue pretty quick right? i dont want to go to the doctor if it's just allergies.",
