      "content": "i'm kinda panicking a bit because the wheezing is getting louder and my chest feels tight. but i really dont want to waste time or money at the er if it's just pollen. i'll just take two zyrtec now to be safe so it works faster, that's fine right? it's better than doing nothing while i wait for the pollen to die down.",
